Games::Console:

2003-03-23 v0.01 Tels - 10 tests - first version
  * Added Games::Console and Games::Console::OpenGL:
    - can move down/up, display messages,
    - shows prompt blinking cursor
    - transparent overlay
2003-04-08 v0.02 Tels - 37 tests
  * fixed doc, documented all functions
  * limit speed, width and height to 0..100
  * enhanced testsuite for more coverage
  * added methods:
    - input(), add_input(), last_input(),
    - autocomplete()
    - backbuffer_size(),
    - prompt(),
    - cursor(),
2003-04-19 v0.03 Tels - 42 tests
  * added the following methods:
    - scroll(), offset()
    - messages(), clear()	

Please send me test-reports, your experiences with this and your ideas - I love
to hear about my work!

